snippet.title: ZooRacers - Multichain Battle Karts - Teaser
snippet.description:
We present you the very first teaser for ZooRacers - Multichain Battle Karts, developed in partnership with YGGDRAZIL.
Stay tuned for more info on this very exciting new Multichain gaming project to be released in 2022.

- Read more about ZooRacers here: https://medium.com/zookeeper-blog/zooracers-general-outline-ff90d1f07427

ZooEcosystem - https://Zoo.One
Yggdrazil - https://www.ygg-cg.com/
